EMRISE CORPORATION ANNOUNCES  DISTRIBUTION TO STOCKHOLDERS OF THIRD LIQUIDATION DIVIDENDWOODBRIDGE, NJ – October 24, 2016 – EMRISE CORPORATION (formerly traded on OTCQB under the symbol EMRI) (EMRISE or the Company), announced today that it has instructed its paying agent, VStock Transfer, LLC (Paying Agent), to begin the process of distributing the previously announced third liquidation dividend of $0.12 per share (the Distribution) to its stockholders of record as of the close of business on July 7, 2015.Read more...
